% Facts defining diseases and their recommended diets
diet(diabetes, 'Low-sugar diet including whole grains, vegetables, lean proteins, and fruits in moderation').
diet(hypertension, 'Low-sodium diet including fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and low-fat dairy').
diet(celiac, 'Gluten-free diet excluding wheat, barley, and rye').
diet(heart_disease, 'Low-fat diet including fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and lean proteins').
diet(obesity, 'Balanced diet with controlled portion sizes and a variety of foods').
diet(kidney_disease, 'Low-protein, low-sodium diet including fruits, vegetables, and controlled portions of dairy and grains').

% Rules to suggest diets based on diseases
suggest_diet(Disease, Diet) :-
    diet(Disease, Diet).

